snippet: Seeking his first PGA Tour victory, Spencer Levin shot a three-under 69 to move into the lead at the Memorial Tournament.
abstract: Golf Roundup; Spencer Levin, seeking his first PGA Tour victory, takes third-round lead at the Memorial Tournament; other golf results noted.
